            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-primary mb-4">About HealthCareSystem</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">We're revolutionizing healthcare delivery through technology. Our platform combines the expertise of qualified medical professionals with cutting-edge AI to provide accessible, efficient, and personalized healthcare services.</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
